WEBVTT

00:08:59.978 --> 00:09:03.287
they risked everything
to save their health institutions.

00:09:03.311 --> 00:09:06.659
The trick for the outsider
who wants to help

00:09:06.683 --> 00:09:09.587
is identifying who those individuals are,

00:09:09.611 --> 00:09:11.919
and building a pathway for them to lead.

00:09:11.943 --> 00:09:15.127
That is exactly what happened
in Afghanistan.

00:09:15.714 --> 00:09:19.043
One of the unsung and untold
success stories

00:09:19.067 --> 00:09:21.985
of our nation-building effort
in Afghanistan

00:09:22.009 --> 00:09:25.505
involved the World Bank in 2002
investing heavily

00:09:25.529 --> 00:09:30.664
in identifying, training and promoting
Afghani health sector leaders.